Job Description
- Provide pre-sales technical support for the product .
- Providing technical support to sales staff and customers and develop pre-sales product configurations/pricing.
- Understanding customer's network environment and deployment plan.
- Providing solution and product recommendations.
- Preparing presentations .
- Participating in evaluations and field trials.
